---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Privacy Policy',
  description: 'How SellOnTube collects, uses, and protects your personal information. Covers data collection, cookies, third-party services, and your privacy rights.',
  robots: { index: true, follow: true },
};

const lastUpdated = '6 March 2026';
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-slate-400 mb-10">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <div class="prose prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Who we are</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            SellOnTube ("we", "us", "our") operates the website at <a href="https://sellontube.com" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">sellontube.com</a>.
            We provide YouTube content strategy and production services for B2B businesses.
            This policy explains what information we collect when you visit our site, how we use it, and your rights.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Information we collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mt-4 mb-2">Information you provide</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            When you book a call through our scheduling link (Cal.com), Cal.com collects your name, email address,
            and any information you choose to share in the booking form. This data is handled under
            <a href="https://cal.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">Cal.com's privacy policy</a>.
            We receive your booking details so we can prepare for and conduct the call.
          </p>

          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mt-4 mb-2">Information collected automatically</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            We use Google Analytics 4 (GA4) to understand how visitors use our site. GA4 automatically collects:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <li>Pages visited and time spent on each page</li>
            <li>Traffic source (how you found us)</li>
            <li>Browser type, device type, and operating system</li>
            <li>General geographic location (country/city level)</li>
            <li>Interactions with page elements</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            GA4 uses cookies and similar tracking technologies. This data is aggregated and does not personally
            identify you. Google Analytics is loaded via Partytown, which runs scripts in a web worker to
            minimise performance impact. Google's data practices are governed by the
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">Google Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Our site uses cookies primarily through Google Analytics. These are analytics cookies that help us
            understand site usage. They do not store personally identifiable information.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            You can disable cookies in your browser settings. Doing so will not affect your ability to use the site,
            though analytics data we receive will be less complete.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">4. How we use your information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <li>To prepare for and conduct diagnostic calls you've booked</li>
            <li>To follow up after calls if you've requested it</li>
            <li>To understand which content and pages are most useful to visitors</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            We do not sell your data. We do not use your information for advertising targeting.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Third-party services</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">The following third-party services are used on this site:</p>
          <div class="mt-3 overflow-x-auto">
            <table class="w-full text-sm text-left text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
              <thead class="bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                <tr>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Service</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Purpose</th>
                  <th class="px-4 py-3 font-semibold">Privacy policy</th>
                </tr>
              </thead>
              <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200 dark:divide-slate-700">
                <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Google Analytics 4</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Site analytics</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3"><a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">policies.google.com</a></td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Cal.com</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Call scheduling</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3"><a href="https://cal.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">cal.com/privacy</a></td>
                </tr>
                <tr class="bg-white dark:bg-slate-900">
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Netlify</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3">Website hosting</td>
                  <td class="px-4 py-3"><a href="https://www.netlify.com/privacy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">netlify.com/privacy</a></td>
                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Data retention</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Google Analytics data is retained for 14 months by default, after which it is automatically deleted.
            Booking and communication data is retained for as long as is necessary to fulfil the purpose
            it was collected for, or as required by law.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Your rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Depending on your location, you may have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1 text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
            <li>Data portability (receive your data in a structured format)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400 mt-3">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@sellontube.com" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">hello@sellontube.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">8. International transfers</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Our site is operated from India. If you are visiting from the European Economic Area or elsewhere,
            your information may be transferred to and processed in countries with different data protection laws.
            By using this site, you consent to this transfer.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Changes to this policy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            We may update this policy occasionally. When we do, we will update the "Last updated" date at the top
            of this page. Continued use of the site after changes constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
            Questions about this policy? Email us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@sellontube.com" class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 hover:underline">hello@sellontube.com</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
